Quickstrike:




Quickstrike was sprawled out on his bunk, arms over his head. He had 
a foot up against the wall, just at the end of his slumber. His 
energy that he needed, being used up from the last fight, traveling, 
and edgy nature was being restored. His mind began to wonder, lifting 
from the strange dream of shadows in the forest and the thing that 
followed. 

He was beinging to wake up.
